<p>How to rewrite if file after <code>stylesheets</code> then read file under specific folder<br> e.g<br> if user visit</p>  <pre><code>domain1.com/stylesheets/index.css actually read  &gt; domain1.com/app/assets/stylesheets/index.css  </code></pre>  <p>or  if visit </p>  <pre><code>domain1.com/stylesheets/bundle/index.css read &gt; domain1.com/app/assets/bundle/stylesheets/index.css </code></pre>  <p>I tried below code but not work...</p>  <pre><code>RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\.)?domain1\.com\.localhost\$ [NC] RewriteRule ^/stylesheets/(.*)\.css$ app/assets/stylesheets/$1 #or this rule not work too RewriteRule ^/stylesheets/$ app/assets/stylesheets/$1   &lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;   DocumentRoot "/Users/username/Sites/domain1.com"   ServerName domain1.com &lt;/VirtualHost&gt; </code></pre>